audio.summary: In this episode of the AWS Rethink podcast, hosts Nolan Chen and Malini Chatterjee welcome back Ben Schneider to discuss AWS Reinvent 2024. Ben, now the head of AI and modern data strategy business development at AWS, shares his exciting experience at the event held in Las Vegas. He describes the incredible energy and enthusiasm among the over 60,000 attendees, partners, and customers. The festive atmosphere was heightened by the Thanksgiving holiday, with the Replay party featuring a roller skating rink and a performance by Weezer. Ben’s recap not only highlights the fun and networking opportunities but also sets the stage for discussing the significant business developments and announcements from AWS Reinvent 2024.
